  <original-body>When trying to use the Rails generators without having Thor installed, you get this message:

@@@
Thor is not available.
If you ran this command from a git checkout of Rails, please make sure thor is installed,
and run this command as `ruby /path/to/rails myapp --dev`
@@@

I've included a patch that simply changes `ruby /path/to/rails myapp --dev` to `ruby /path/to/rails new myapp --dev` (adding &quot;new&quot;). :)</original-body>
